	(text "V_{BUS} comes from the USB 5V. If present, the gate of\nD_{1} will be high, preventing power from reaching V_{SYS}.\nThis allows it to be powered from either USB or the MEAN WELL.\n\nThis FET has a low on resistance."
		(exclude_from_sim yes)
